narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes. Whether you know a lot or a little going in, you will leave with a solid understanding of North Korea.
Good class to learn about the subject matter, a bit dry at times. I have confidence it will be better the second time around.
Yes. I will recommend it to other students.
